Universal Job Application System - Complete Field Library
A. Personal Information Section
1. Basic Contact Information
Salutation (Mr., Mrs., Ms., Mx., Dr., Prof., Other)

First Name (Legal)

Middle Name (Optional)

Last Name (Legal)

Preferred First Name (Optional)

Email Address (Primary)

Alternate Email Address (Optional)

Mobile Phone Number (Primary)

Home Phone Number (Optional)

Work Phone Number (Optional)

Preferred Contact Method (Email, Phone, Text)

Best Time to Contact (Morning, Afternoon, Evening, Any)

2. Address Information
Current Address Line 1

Current Address Line 2 (Apartment, Suite, Unit)

City

State/Province

ZIP/Postal Code

Country

Address Type (Home, Temporary, Permanent)

Years at Current Address

Previous Address (if less than X years at current)

Same as Mailing Address? (Checkbox for additional fields)

3. Demographic Information (Voluntary - EEO Reporting)
Gender Identity (Male, Female, Non-binary, Prefer not to say, Prefer to self-describe)

Date of Birth (MM/DD/YYYY)

Ethnicity/Race (For EEO-1 reporting: White, Black/African American, Hispanic/Latino, Asian, Native American, Pacific Islander, Two or more races, Prefer not to answer)

Veteran Status (Protected Veteran, Disabled Veteran, Recently Separated Veteran, Active Duty Wartime, Other Protected Veteran, Non-Veteran, Prefer not to say)

Disability Status (Yes, No, Prefer not to say - ADA Section 503)

Work Authorization (US Citizen, Permanent Resident, Visa Type, Requires Sponsorship)

B. Employment Information
4. Work Authorization & Eligibility
Are you legally authorized to work in [Country]? (Yes/No)

Will you now or in the future require visa sponsorship? (Yes/No)

If you have a visa, provide type and expiration date

Have you ever been convicted of a felony? (Yes/No - with explanation field if yes)

Are you willing to undergo a background check? (Yes/No)

Are you willing to take a drug test? (Yes/No if relevant to position)

5. Employment Preferences
Desired Job Title/Role

Employment Type Desired (Full-time, Part-time, Contract, Temporary, Internship, Seasonal)

Work Schedule Preference (Days, Evenings, Nights, Weekends, Rotating, Flexible)

Shift Availability (First, Second, Third, Any)

Willing to Work Overtime? (Yes/No/Occasionally)

Minimum Acceptable Salary/Wage (Hourly/Annual)

Desired Salary Range (From - To)

Willing to Relocate? (Yes/No)

If yes, relocation radius (Miles/Kilometers)

Available Start Date

Notice Period Required (If currently employed)

Referred by Employee (Name/ID if applicable)

How did you hear about this position? (Company Website, Indeed, LinkedIn, Referral, Job Fair, Social Media, Other)

C. Education History Section
6. Educational Background
(Repeatable section for each institution)

Institution Name

Institution Type (High School, College/University, Technical School, Trade School, Online)

Location (City, State, Country)

Degree/Certificate Earned (Diploma, Associate, Bachelor, Master, PhD, Certificate, Other)

Field of Study/Major

Minor/Concentration (Optional)

GPA (on 4.0 scale or other)

Graduation Date (Month/Year)

Expected Graduation Date (If still attending)

Currently Attending? (Yes/No)

Honors/Awards (Summa Cum Laude, Dean's List, etc.)

Relevant Coursework (List or upload transcript)

Education Verification Consent (Yes/No)

7. Licenses & Certifications
(Repeatable section)

License/Certification Name

