Reference Check Authorization

Data Privacy Consent (GDPR/CCPA compliant)

Electronic Signature Consent

Equal Opportunity Acknowledgement

Arbitration Agreement (If required by company)

Employee Handbook Acknowledgement (Will read if hired)

